      <p><strong>A note on affiliate marketing and email platforms:</strong> Some email marketing platforms restrict promotional affiliate content or apply strict guidelines around what you can send. Platforms with more permissive affiliate-friendly policies include GetResponse, AWeber, and Systeme.io. ConvertKit and MailerLite permit affiliate links but require compliance with their terms. Always read the acceptable use policy of your chosen platform before building on it.</p>

